   "text": "• per-engineer SDLC pipelines (8 stage classes,\n  Debate/MoA/Voting, DAG/swarm)\n• proving ground: patterns & skills iterate here\n• SDLC standard ADR-0003: class R0 default,\n  auto-escalates on workspace/sandbox/deploy\n  [live]",
