  {
   "id": "text-5602",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 1525,
   "y": 1922,
   "width": 348.74,
   "height": 280.0,
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 1,
   "opacity": 100,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 173662,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 543394,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "boundElements": null,
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "INTAKE — how orders arrive:  [mockup]\n  • human orders (console / backlog)\n  • incident-spawned P0 tasks from AI SRE\n    (permanent-fix chase, incident_id→task_id)\n  • Mode A: pre-approved templates (cron/drift)\n  • Mode B: research → ranked hypotheses\n    to a human (cannot create tasks itself)\n\nConductor FSM: TRIGGERED→PLANNING→CLASSIFIED\n  →RUNNING→VERIFYING→DRAFT_PR→PARKED/MERGED\nWorker (family A) ≠ Evaluator (family B),\n  dual sandbox, proofs A/A′/B/E, canaries\ncan_auto_merge: 7 conditions, fail-closed,\n  prod never auto\nRollback: saga compensators + git revert;\n  ephemeral env is the sandbox rollback",
   "fontSize": 14,
   "fontFamily": 6,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 14,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "INTAKE — how orders arrive:  [mockup]\n  • human orders (console / backlog)\n  • incident-spawned P0 tasks from AI SRE\n    (permanent-fix chase, incident_id→task_id)\n  • Mode A: pre-approved templates (cron/drift)\n  • Mode B: research → ranked hypotheses\n    to a human (cannot create tasks itself)\n\nConductor FSM: TRIGGERED→PLANNING→CLASSIFIED\n  →RUNNING→VERIFYING→DRAFT_PR→PARKED/MERGED\nWorker (family A) ≠ Evaluator (family B),\n  dual sandbox, proofs A/A′/B/E, canaries\ncan_auto_merge: 7 conditions, fail-closed,\n  prod never auto\nRollback: saga compensators + git revert;\n  ephemeral env is the sandbox rollback",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
